Maximizar z=100x1+30x2		z-100x1-30x2 = 0

x1+x2 <= 7			x1+x2+s1 = 7
10x1 + 4x2 <= 40	10x1+4x2+s2 = 40
xi >= 0

|-----+------+-----+----+----+--------+-----|
|     | x1   | x2  | s1 | s2 | result | piv |
|-----+------+-----+----+----+--------+-----|
| s1  | 1    | 1   | 1  | 0  | 7      |     |
| s2  | 10   | 4   | 0  | 1  | 40     | x   | *(1/10) |
| z   | -100 | -30 | 0  | 0  | 0      |     |
|-----+------+-----+----+----+--------+-----|
| piv | x    |     |    |    |        |     |
|-----+------+-----+----+----+--------+-----|

|-----+----+-----+----+-------+--------+-----+-----------|
|     | x1 | x2  | s1 | s2    | result | piv | operation |
|-----+----+-----+----+-------+--------+-----+-----------|
| s1  | 0  | 3/5 | 1  | -1/10 | 3      |     | *(-1)+s1  |
| x1  | 1  | 2/5 | 0  | 1/10  | 4      |     |           |
| z   | 0  | 10  | 0  | 10    | 400    |     | *100+z    |
|-----+----+-----+----+-------+--------+-----+-----------|
| piv |    |     |    |       |        |     |           |
|-----+----+-----+----+-------+--------+-----+-----------|

x1=4
x2=0
z=400
